### Test: $lookup (no valid codes — content=not-present, ETL-populated)
# This CodeSystem has content=not-present. No concepts are defined in the FSH source.
# Concepts are expected to be loaded via ETL from official eGK-VSD specifications.
# RESULT: 0 concepts in Aidbox (expected for not-present CodeSystem without ETL data)
GET http://localhost:8080/fhir/CodeSystem/$lookup?system=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/CodeSystem/zuzahlungsstatus&code=INVALID_XYZ
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

### Workaround: Aidbox Concept API — count all concepts
# Expected: 0 (no ETL data loaded)
# RESULT: PASS — total=0
GET http://localhost:8080/Concept?system=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/CodeSystem/zuzahlungsstatus&_count=0
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

### Workaround: Aidbox Concept API — verify INVALID_XYZ not found
# RESULT: PASS
GET http://localhost:8080/Concept?system=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/CodeSystem/zuzahlungsstatus&code=INVALID_XYZ&_count=1
Authorization: Basic basic:secret
